msgctxt "indexentry|extended_tip|key1cb"
msgid "Makes the current selection a subentry of the word that you enter here. For example, if you select “cold”, and enter “weather” as the 1st key, the index entry will be “weather, cold”."
msgstr "Déanann sé seo fo-iontráil den rogha reatha den fhocal a iontrálann tú anseo. Mar shampla, má roghnaíonn tú “fuar”, agus má iontrálann tú “aimsir” mar an chéad eochair, beidh an iontráil innéacs “aimsir, fuar”."

#. TszYK
#: sw/uiconfig/swriter/ui/indexentry.ui:389
msgctxt "indexentry|key2ft"
msgid "2nd key:"
msgstr "2ú eochair:"

