msgid "Makes the current selection a sub-subentry of the 1st key. For example, if you select “cold”, and enter “weather” as the 1st key and “winter” as the 2nd key, the index entry will be “weather, winter, cold”."
msgstr "Déanann sé seo fo-iontráil den chéad eochair den rogha reatha. Mar shampla, má roghnaíonn tú “fuar”, agus má iontrálann tú “aimsir” mar an chéad eochair agus “geimhreadh” mar an dara heochair, beidh an iontráil innéacs “aimsir, geimhreadh, fuar”."

