#. wes3j
#: sw/uiconfig/swriter/ui/tocindexpage.ui:859
msgctxt "tocindexpage|extended_tip|combinesame"
msgid "Replaces identical index entries with a single entry that lists the page numbers where the entry occurs in the document. For example, the entries “View 10, View 43” are combined as “View 10, 43”."
msgstr "Cuireann sé iontráil aonair in ionad iontrálacha innéacs comhionanna ina liostaítear uimhreacha na leathanach ina bhfuil an iontráil sa doiciméad. Mar shampla, cuirtear na hiontrálacha “Radharc 10, Radharc 43” le chéile mar “Radharc 10, 43”."

#. AVAFm
#: sw/uiconfig/swriter/ui/tocindexpage.ui:870
msgctxt "tocindexpage|useff"
msgid "Combine identical entries with f. or _ff."
msgstr "Cuir iontrálacha comhionanna le chéile le f. nó _ff."

#. 4SLZc
#: sw/uiconfig/swriter/ui/tocindexpage.ui:879
msgctxt "tocindexpage|extended_tip|useff"
msgid "Replaces identical index entries that occur on the directly following page(s), with a single entry that lists the first page number and a “f” or “ff”. For example, the entries “View 10, View 11” are combined as “View 10f”, and “View 10, View 11, View 12” as “View 10ff”. Actual appearance depends on the locale setting, but can be overridden with Sort - Language."
msgstr "Cuireann sé seo iontrálacha innéacs comhionanna in ionad na leathanach/leathanaigh díreach ina dhiaidh sin, le hiontráil aonair ina liostaítear an chéad uimhir leathanaigh agus “f” nó “ff”. Mar shampla, cuirtear na hiontrálacha “Radharc 10, Radharc 11” le chéile mar “Radharc 10f”, agus “Radharc 10, Radharc 11, Radharc 12” mar “Radharc 10ff”. Braitheann an chuma iarbhír ar an socrú logála, ach is féidir é a shárú le Sórtáil - Teanga."

#. Uivc8
